otherFacts.value: Club House, Playground, Pool, Green Areas, Lake/Pond, Recreation Room

data.description: This is a cute 1500 sf  home in the pines....very nice layout in here with a spacious kitchen and dining nook, separate laundry area and open living room. Floorplan is split, 2 guest br on one end with Master on the other, beautiful fireplace in the living room and a great location with convenient access to town, WITH a garage! There is some deferred maintenance which does not appear to be major; bring your skills and dress this cutie up for a rental or personal existence!
data.whatILove: This home is located in a convenient area for access to Cripple Creek; mountain adventure and the subdivision has a clubhouse with a heated pool, playground, lots of greenbelt & picnic areas, dotted with ponds. Its beautiful, bucolic and loaded with wildlife! The home does exhibit signs of deferred maintenance, nothing major jumps out at me so it is listed as a Renovators Special. Will  make a great family home or rental, good bones here!
